commit 43c734be5571a4daad9f0a3e0b3229a1c0049917 upstream.

This patch fixes L2 Cache size calculations for L2C-210, L2C-310 and
PL310, by changing the L2X0_AUX_CTRL_WAY_SIZE_MASK from 2 bits to 3
