The following race can occur with qdio devices that use the shared device
state change indicator:

Device (Shared DSCI)    CPU0                            CPU1
===============================================================================

1. DSCI 0 => 1,
   INT pending
                        2. Thinint handler
                        * si_used = 1
                        * Inbound tasklet_schedule
                        * DSCI 1 => 0

3. DSCI 0 => 1,
   INT pending

